Excuse me, I was in high school.

374
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,030
就知道学习  洁身自爱
Studying, keeping my nose clean,

375
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:27,170
在社区做志愿服务
doing volunteer work for the community.

376
00:18:30,210 --> 00:18:32,040
没怀孕
Not pregnant.

377
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,580
太好了
Yes!

378
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:41,890
乌班图
Oh, Ubuntu,

379
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:46,090
